(A4: This project delivers an interactive aviation anomaly-monitoring prototype that combines) Tj
0 -15 Td
(    simulation, online learning, and an operational dashboard. On the frontend, a Flask web) Tj
0 -15 Td
(    interface presents three synchronized views: \(1\) flight path and route behavior on a live) Tj
0 -15 Td
(    map, \(2\) engine and subsystem health from telemetry-style sensor signals, and \(3\) airspace) Tj
0 -15 Td
(    condition awareness using corridor status and bulletin-style risk events. On the backend, a) Tj
0 -15 Td
(    streaming simulation engine generates time-series data every second from seeded) Tj
0 -15 Td
(    route/sensor/news baselines plus stochastic variation and user-driven stress controls. The) Tj
0 -15 Td
(    machine-learning layer uses incremental training with scikit-learn SGDClassifier models to) Tj
0 -15 Td
(    continuously update risk estimation for path, engine, and airspace signals. A lightweight) Tj
0 -15 Td
(    autoencoder-style neural component adds reconstruction-error scoring for engine behavior,) Tj
